xyz.acygn.mokapot.wireformat

Class SaltedObjectMethodDatabase<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.acygn.mokapot.util.ObjectMethodDatabase<T>
      • xyz.acygn.mokapot.wireformat.SaltedObjectMethodDatabase<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The actual class of objects described by the database.

    public class SaltedObjectMethodDatabase<T>
extends ObjectMethodDatabase<T>
    An ObjectMethodDatabase that, additionally, calculates a salt for method code calculation that ensures that there will be no clashes between method codes of the class's methods.
    Author:
    Alex Smith
